00:03:57.520 --> 00:03:58.930
from a drive-through window.

00:03:58.930 --> 00:04:00.920
I mean, there was stuff
coming out of them,

00:04:00.920 --> 00:04:04.210
and lettuce and
things like that.

00:04:04.210 --> 00:04:06.550
And they were kind
of a disaster.

00:04:06.550 --> 00:04:09.110
And then we went in and talked
to focus groups about what

00:04:09.110 --> 00:04:12.240
people wanted from a hamburger.

00:04:12.240 --> 00:04:14.820
