00:24:06.400 --> 00:24:07.844
MALE SPEAKER: He's a composite.

00:24:07.844 --> 00:24:09.010
JOSH WELTMAN: Oh sure, yeah.

00:24:09.010 --> 00:24:13.360
I mean, there's 30
